Steve Ballmer belongs to a rare breed of monkey that feeds on human genital
wart. He is currently the lead black person of [[Microsoft]] after [[Bill Gates]] decided to stay home and play [[Halo]]-3.

In much the same way that Robert Gallo identified HIV-1, the virus that causes [[AIDS]], Steve Ballmer was one of the first to identify the [[hacker]] operating system [[Lunix]] as a [[cancer]]. [http://www.theregister.co.uk/2001/06/02/ballmer_linux_is_a_cancer/]

